Deadmau5 - While (Kingdomleaks Edition) (DEMO VERSION) 

               Electronica, Dubstep, IBM | Mau5trap Recordings

             320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 02:28:15 | 341 Mb


From the words of Negatron (Thank you <3) "I compiled all of Joel's songs from his fanclub and soundcloud (which has been unavailable for a few months now) into a near perfect mock-up/advance of his new album. Some are masters, some are demos, some are placeholders, but it's all fresh, deceased rodent tunes. From one mau5head to many, here is while(1<2): Demo Edition." Kingdom Leaks is a site dedicated to bringing you the most recent albums on release day, or when they leak early, so that YOU can decide if it's worth buying or not.
